{{Orphan|date=June 2018}}
Many musicians have been killed during their active career. Some of them have received extensive media attention, including the [[murder of John Lennon]] in 1980 and the murder of rappers [[Tupac murder|Tupac]] and [[Murder of Christopher Wallace|Biggie Smalls]] less than one year apart. Others have received less media attention, including the murder of [[Bryan Harvey (musician)|Bryan Harvey]], who was killed during the [[2006 Richmond spree murders]].
[[Christina_Grimmie|Christina Grimmie]]'s shooting murder became more publicized because the [[Pulse nightclub shooting]] occurred the following night and also took place in [[Orlando, Florida]]. {{-}}
